00:04:32.678 --> 00:04:35.169
Arn LICHTENSTEIN, oykhet fun Pshedbuzh

00:04:35.749 --> 00:04:38.358
un ikh ho- ikh zol kenen hobn a bisl esn.

00:04:39.073 --> 00:04:41.952
