00:08:31.864 --> 00:08:33.883
bin ikh shoyn nisht geven keyn religyezer.

00:08:35.424 --> 00:08:37.848
bist geshlofn in a bet f- aleyn?

00:08:37.482 --> 00:08:38.353
neyn.

