00:08:42.006 --> 00:08:43.924
geven, ikh veys

00:08:44.233 --> 00:08:45.999
tsvey kinder zenen gevezn

00:08:47.288 --> 00:08:49.191
azoy hot oysge⟨UNK⟩ dos lebn.

00:08:49.191 --> 00:08:50.229
s'iz afilet

00:08:50.229 --> 00:08:53.812
keyn matrats nisht gevezn. arayngeleygt shtroy

00:08:53.886 --> 00:08:58.706
un m'hot tsekopet di shtroy, un in di fri hot men gedorfn dos oyfroymen.

00:08:59.455 --> 00:09:04.174
s'iz nisht geven dos yetsike lebn. s'iz geven zeyer a fintster, farbitert lebn.

00:09:05.462 --> 00:09:06.637
zeyer orem.

00:09:06.762 --> 00:09:07.971
