00:09:37.997 --> 00:09:39.256
dos gedenk ikh.

00:09:40.984 --> 00:09:44.336
un, un vos hostu gebrent? ho- holts oder koyln?

00:09:44.038 --> 00:09:46.344
holts, torf

00:09:47.143 --> 00:09:49.617
shteyn koyln hot men nisht gekent brenen in dem.

00:09:49.725 --> 00:09:51.356
holts mit torf.

00:09:52.273 --> 00:09:56.722
m'hot ge- m'hot gekoyft a vogn holts hot men gekoyft in, in di gas

00:09:57.015 --> 00:10:00.657
un s'iz gekumen a poyer fun dorf un hot dos tsehakt

00:10:00.657 --> 00:10:02.544
