00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:06.476
du host tsugeholfn di mame in kikh?

00:10:06.668 --> 00:10:07.455
neyn.

00:10:11.713 --> 00:10:15.228
un di, di ontuekhts, zaynen zey geven

00:10:15.228 --> 00:10:16.753
reyn? z-

