00:10:58.491 --> 00:11:00.273
a biter lebn hot men gemakht.

00:11:01.663 --> 00:11:03.187
s'iz gevezn

00:11:03.187 --> 00:11:05.269
a fuftsn pro- protsent

00:11:05.275 --> 00:11:07.297
fun ba- yidishn bafelkerung

00:11:07.297 --> 00:11:09.133
vos zenen geven farmeglekh

00:11:09.291 --> 00:11:12.812
ober akhtsik, finef un akhtsik protsent iz geven oreme mentshn.

00:11:13.003 --> 00:11:15.494
