00:11:31.482 --> 00:11:33.264
di kinder zenen gevezn

00:11:33.321 --> 00:11:35.241
eyner iz gevezn in

00:11:35.241 --> 00:11:38.478
in Luksemburg. eyner iz gevezn andersh vu

00:11:38.637 --> 00:11:40.791
in Varshe. zey hobn gearbet

00:11:40.881 --> 00:11:42.439
oyf postns

00:11:42.439 --> 00:11:46.123
in di heym hobn zey nisht gekent zayn, vayl in di heym hobn mir nisht gehat keyn esn.

00:11:47.648 --> 00:11:50.274
vos far a shtot iz geven Pshedbuzh?

00:11:50.652 --> 00:11:53.886
Pshedbuzh, dos hot geheysn di shtot

00:11:54.128 --> 00:11:56.029
PRZED BORZ

00:11:56.541 --> 00:11:59.555
farn vald. BORZ iz a vald

00:11:59.713 --> 00:12:02.326
hot men a nomen gegebn dos shtetl, hot men a nomen gegebn

00:12:02.326 --> 00:12:06.047
PRZED BORZ, farn vald. dort iz geven shtendik a vald.

00:12:06.047 --> 00:12:09.295
dos vald iz gevorn oysgehakt. m'hot gemakht a shtetl fun dem.

00:12:09.295 --> 00:12:10.840
ot derfar hot dos geheysn

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:12.060
Pshedbuzh.

00:12:13.197 --> 00:12:18.540
un vos gedenkstu iz forgekumen in Pshedbuzh, tsvishn di yidn in Pshedbuzh?

00:12:18.529 --> 00:12:20.227
vos ikh gedenk

00:12:20.824 --> 00:12:23.265
ikh gedenk az shtendik

00:12:23.305 --> 00:12:25.121
hot men undz gehaltn

00:12:26.055 --> 00:12:28.479
m'hot gehat antisemitn zeyer a sakh.

00:12:29.076 --> 00:12:31.264
yidishe kinder mit goyishe

00:12:31.303 --> 00:12:33.457
hobn zikh zeyer veynik gekhavert

00:12:33.835 --> 00:12:36.883
far m'hot zey gelernt in di shule hot men zey gelernt

00:12:37.497 --> 00:12:38.767
az yidn

00:12:38.767 --> 00:12:40.831
hobn geharget JESUSn.

00:12:41.327 --> 00:12:45.135
m'hot geharget goyishe kinder. m'hot genumen dos blut oyf matses.

00:12:45.192 --> 00:12:50.150
dos iz gegan in di, in di goyishe kinder, kristlekhn kinder

00:12:50.150 --> 00:12:52.138
iz dos geganen in gedank arayn

00:12:52.161 --> 00:12:54.872
un dos i- hot gebrengt dos antisemitizm.

00:12:55.367 --> 00:13:01.790
v- ven bist a bisl elter gevorn, hostu zikh ongehoybn khavern mit di, mit di

00:13:01.881 --> 00:13:06.198
⟨dos⟩ hob ikh shoyn gehat mayn svive, hob ikh shoyn gehat mayne khaveyrim yidishe khevre.

00:13:01.915 --> 00:13:03.107
nisht yi-

00:13:06.198 --> 00:13:08.237
kh'hob mikh keyn molt mit zey gekhavert

00:13:09.542 --> 00:13:10.490
keyn molt nisht.

00:13:10.302 --> 00:13:12.473
s'iz geven a sakh yidn in Pshedbuzh?

00:13:12.597 --> 00:13:15.460
in Pshedbuzh hobn gevoynt zekhtsik protsent yidn.

00:13:15.651 --> 00:13:17.180
Pshedbuzh iz geven

00:13:17.322 --> 00:13:18.835
tsvey teyln.

00:13:19.617 --> 00:13:21.703
s'iz gevezn Pshedbuzh.

00:13:22.182 --> 00:13:23.697
in di mit iz geven

00:13:23.697 --> 00:13:26.394
a holtserne brik. geven a PILICA

00:13:26.620 --> 00:13:28.031
vos iz geganen

00:13:28.071 --> 00:13:31.339
arayn keyn Varshe. dos vaser iz geganen keyn Varshe

00:13:32.188 --> 00:13:35.776
un iber di PILICA iz gevorn geleygt a holtserne brik

00:13:35.952 --> 00:13:40.806
aribertsugeyn. geven dort a shtetele, Vidame hot dos geheysn. geven an opteylung.

00:13:40.997 --> 00:13:42.425
dort iz oykh geven

00:13:42.550 --> 00:13:43.371
yidn.

00:13:44.203 --> 00:13:45.564
dos iz geven der Pshedbuzh.

00:13:45.891 --> 00:13:47.255
Pshedbuzh iz geven

00:13:47.255 --> 00:13:50.663
s'iz nisht geven, anfang, s'iz nisht geven keyn shtot, keyn shtetl

00:13:50.663 --> 00:13:52.010
nor s'iz geven a vald.

00:13:55.290 --> 00:13:57.494
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn

00:13:59.003 --> 00:14:05.325
di daytshe makht, di natsi makht in Daytshland, vos, vos hostu gehert f- derfun?

00:14:05.128 --> 00:14:08.547
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn fun dray un draysikstn yor

00:14:08.959 --> 00:14:11.467
hobn zey gegrindet in Poyln

00:14:11.592 --> 00:14:13.577
a fashistishe partey.

00:14:14.190 --> 00:14:16.124
natsyonale partey.

00:14:16.587 --> 00:14:19.129
ongehoybn tsu kemfn mit di yidn

00:14:19.675 --> 00:14:21.351
aroysgeshribn

00:14:21.351 --> 00:14:22.909
plakatn oyf di vent

00:14:23.235 --> 00:14:25.068
NIE KUPUJ U ZYDA

00:14:25.429 --> 00:14:27.144
UNK ZYDAMI

00:14:27.370 --> 00:14:29.729
zenen geshtanen azoy UNK oyfn mark

00:14:29.729 --> 00:14:31.144
dinstik oyfn torg

00:14:31.217 --> 00:14:34.282
un nisht gelozt tsugeyn di poyerim, zoln koyfn bay a yid

00:14:34.474 --> 00:14:35.694
un davke

00:14:35.694 --> 00:14:38.096
hobn zey yo gekoyft. UNK far vos?

00:14:38.102 --> 00:14:40.053
bay a yid hobn zey gekoyft biliker.

00:14:40.752 --> 00:14:42.613
mit di yidn hobn zey nisht gekent

00:14:42.613 --> 00:14:44.390
makhn keyn COMPETITION.

00:14:45.207 --> 00:14:48.485
dos iz geven di eyntsike tsore far zey

00:14:48.485 --> 00:14:51.714
vos zey hobn nisht gekent firn keyn BUSINESS

00:14:51.940 --> 00:14:53.132
in dem shtetl

00:14:54.066 --> 00:14:56.304
vayl zey hobn gevolt a sakh fardinen

00:14:56.547 --> 00:14:58.076
veynik farkoyfn

00:14:58.251 --> 00:15:01.074
un bay yidn iz geven andersh. yidn hobn farshtanen

00:15:01.074 --> 00:15:03.813
az me darf leyzn. az me leyzt a sakh

00:15:03.904 --> 00:15:05.956
kumt arayn mer INCOME.

00:15:05.963 --> 00:15:07.425
glaykht zikh oys.

00:15:07.431 --> 00:15:09.368
un az me vart az s'vet zayn

00:15:09.368 --> 00:15:12.718
m'vet nemen a ⟨PRICE⟩, leyzt men gornisht. nishto keyn INCOME

00:15:12.718 --> 00:15:15.930
un me leyzt nisht. dos iz geven di gantse tsore bay zey

00:15:15.970 --> 00:15:19.406
far derfar hot men zey nisht gelitn, un zey hobn undz nisht gelitn.

00:15:19.665 --> 00:15:20.756
in

00:15:21.285 --> 00:15:22.865
di groyse shtet

00:15:23.310 --> 00:15:26.783
hobn yidn nisht gekent arayngeyn arbetn afile

00:15:26.783 --> 00:15:27.911
bar a yid.

00:15:28.339 --> 00:15:30.268
s'iz geven an Osher Korn

00:15:30.268 --> 00:15:31.725
vos hot basheftikt

00:15:31.967 --> 00:15:35.066
hunderter, hunderter mentshn, toyznter ken men zogn.

00:15:35.207 --> 00:15:37.026
s'iz geven a POZNANSKI.

00:15:37.026 --> 00:15:40.449
es hobn gearbet bay im ⟨vos⟩ a fuftsn toyznt mentshn

00:15:40.692 --> 00:15:42.407
a yidisher fabrikant

00:15:42.666 --> 00:15:44.668
un keyn yid hot dort nisht gekent arbetn

00:15:45.197 --> 00:15:46.620
vayl s'hot geheysn

00:15:46.620 --> 00:15:50.287
der ZWIAZEK ZAWODOWA, dos hot geheysn di IRGUN, nu

00:15:50.783 --> 00:15:53.510
do iz geven di UN- do heyst es di, di UNION.

00:15:54.023 --> 00:15:58.640
hot men nisht tsugelozt zol arbetn in di fabrikn, veln arbetn yidn

00:16:01.127 --> 00:16:04.040
un s'iz geven a groyse arbetsloze, gedenk ikh

00:16:04.367 --> 00:16:06.116
zeyer groyse arbetsloze

00:16:07.050 --> 00:16:09.170
un s'iz geven groyse tsores.

00:16:09.700 --> 00:16:12.295
un azoy vi s'hot zikh ongehoybn di, di

00:16:12.295 --> 00:16:13.845
di Hitler makht

00:16:13.986 --> 00:16:16.882
hobn zey gegrindet dortn in Poyln a partey

00:16:17.445 --> 00:16:20.358
un m'hot undz gemakht tsores.

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:22.434
m'iz ongefaln oyf di nakht

00:16:22.643 --> 00:16:23.930
oyf yidn

00:16:23.930 --> 00:16:27.378
ver s'hot zikh gekent shteln a vidershtand hot geshtelt a vidershtand.

00:16:27.553 --> 00:16:29.338
m'hot zikh nisht gelozt fun zey

00:16:29.338 --> 00:16:32.626
dos iz geven azoy lang biz di milkhome hot oysgebrokhn.

00:16:32.278 --> 00:16:34.477
d- du host aleyn

00:16:34.477 --> 00:16:38.094
gezen azelkhe f- faln vos m'hot, m'iz umge-

00:16:37.307 --> 00:16:41.030
yo. ikh hob gearbet bay eynemen. in Lodzh hob ikh gearbet bar eynemen.

00:16:41.374 --> 00:16:42.988
dos iz gevezn

00:16:43.281 --> 00:16:47.105
in zeks un dray- in zibn un draysikstn yor

00:16:47.247 --> 00:16:51.122
hot mit mir gearbet dort a, mayns a kuzin, ⟨JEDZYNSKI⟩

00:16:52.039 --> 00:16:54.429
iz er aheymgekumen mit a ⟨tseblutn⟩ kop

00:16:56.089 --> 00:16:59.407
⟨gezogt⟩ m'hot im ongefaln oyfn veg. m'hot im tsehakt dem kop mit a shteyn.

00:17:04.054 --> 00:17:09.937
un in, in di heym ho- hostu geredt mit di, mit di familye vegn di zakhn?

00:17:09.943 --> 00:17:10.848
neyn.

00:17:11.714 --> 00:17:13.885
dos bin ikh shoyn nisht geven damolt in di heym.

00:17:14.382 --> 00:17:16.890
in Pshedbuzh, ven ikh bin gevezn

00:17:18.972 --> 00:17:21.649
m'hot undz a molt opgevart. m'hot undz

00:17:21.857 --> 00:17:23.218
m'iz bafaln

00:17:23.376 --> 00:17:25.952
fun tsayt tsu tsayt, ober m'hot zikh nisht gelozt.

00:17:26.498 --> 00:17:28.196
m'hot geshtelt a vidershtand.

00:17:29.316 --> 00:17:32.212
s'iz geven UNK. s'iz geven khuliganes

00:17:32.218 --> 00:17:33.764
ober m'hot zikh nisht gelozt.

00:17:33.940 --> 00:17:35.463
ales far derfar

00:17:35.463 --> 00:17:36.700
far m'iz yidn.

00:17:37.753 --> 00:17:39.350
un di politsey

00:17:39.525 --> 00:17:41.864
hot nisht ge- hot gornisht getun vegn dem.

00:17:41.888 --> 00:17:44.042
vos far a vidershtand hostu geshtelt?

00:17:43.896 --> 00:17:45.257
m'hot zikh nisht gelozt

00:17:47.254 --> 00:17:48.496
vi du folgst.

00:17:49.347 --> 00:17:51.315
vos hostu genitst, shtekns?

00:17:50.848 --> 00:17:52.394
NO, NO

00:17:52.435 --> 00:17:54.758
s'iz a molt, s'iz a molt ongefaln

00:17:55.506 --> 00:18:01.372
eyner a khuligan, zenen mir geven dray yidn. m'hot im gut tsehakt, un m'iz antlofn fertik.

00:18:05.277 --> 00:18:08.578
host moyre gehat az di daytshn veln araynkumen in Poyln?

00:18:09.664 --> 00:18:13.238
damolt ven di daytshn hobn gevolt araynkumen

00:18:13.238 --> 00:18:16.019
bin ikh shoyn nisht geven in Pshedbuzh, bin ikh shoyn geven in Lodzh.

00:18:15.925 --> 00:18:16.644
yo

00:18:16.482 --> 00:18:19.128
ikh hob nisht far- kh'hob nisht getrakht vegn dem

00:18:19.128 --> 00:18:20.727
az s'vet zayn azoy shlekht

00:18:22.928 --> 00:18:26.854
di daytshn zenen, eyder ⟨zey⟩ zenen arayngekumen, bin ikh in gantsn geven in Lodzh

00:18:26.927 --> 00:18:28.895
tsvey un a halb yor.

00:18:29.526 --> 00:18:32.456
kh'hob gearbet. beyde hot men gearbet, ikh mit di froy

00:18:32.665 --> 00:18:35.055
un m'hot gehat fil veynik parnose.

00:18:35.770 --> 00:18:38.126
nu, ven di daytshn ⟨zenen⟩ arayngekumen

00:18:38.149 --> 00:18:39.965
hot dos ales geendert.

00:18:39.567 --> 00:18:40.337
yo

00:18:40.613 --> 00:18:42.885
di froy hot mir shoyn nisht gelozt in di gasn arayn.

00:18:43.431 --> 00:18:45.365
zi hot mikh bahaltn in di shtub

00:18:46.502 --> 00:18:49.921
un zi hot shoyn geshafn di parnose, ayngekoyft.

00:18:49.995 --> 00:18:54.748
ven bist nokh geven in Pshedbuzh, bist gang in shule tsvey yor bloyz?

00:18:53.877 --> 00:18:54.782
yo

00:18:55.108 --> 00:18:56.756
vos gedenkstu fun di shule?

00:18:56.610 --> 00:18:57.616
gornisht.

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:02.201
gornisht. damolt ven m- s'iz gekumen

00:19:02.201 --> 00:19:04.147
a MEMBER fun CHURCH

00:19:05.301 --> 00:19:08.332
gebn zey a halbe sho oder a sho a lektsye

00:19:08.524 --> 00:19:10.022
zeyer religye

00:19:10.022 --> 00:19:11.505
iz bay undz nisht gevezn.

00:19:11.562 --> 00:19:14.115
UNK undz arayngegangen. zey hobn gehat bazundere

00:19:14.115 --> 00:19:15.403
a lektsye

00:19:16.303 --> 00:19:17.512
fun religye.

00:19:18.852 --> 00:19:20.702
dos hot men undz shoyn nisht gekent hern

00:19:21.062 --> 00:19:23.705
nor zey hobn undz shtendik forgevorfn

00:19:23.813 --> 00:19:25.764
"ZYDZI DO PALESTYNY"

00:19:29.095 --> 00:19:31.316
dos iz gevezn, als kinder oykhet.

00:19:33.550 --> 00:19:36.463
in velkhe shprakh hostu gelernt in shule?

00:19:36.958 --> 00:19:38.049
poylish

00:19:38.578 --> 00:19:40.428
in di heym hostu geredt poylish?

00:19:40.013 --> 00:19:40.952
neyn.

00:19:41.278 --> 00:19:42.774
in di heym hot geredt yidish.

00:19:42.358 --> 00:19:44.664
fun vanet hostu zikh oysgelernt poylish?

00:19:44.738 --> 00:19:47.089
fun di shule UNK poylish, bin ikh gevezn

00:19:47.089 --> 00:19:49.052
bin dokh geven biz in

00:19:49.378 --> 00:19:52.168
biz in nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:19:52.168 --> 00:19:53.287
geven a kind

00:19:53.462 --> 00:19:55.160
ken men zikh nisht oyslernen.

00:19:55.302 --> 00:19:55.920
nu, yo

00:19:55.302 --> 00:19:57.354
s'iz geven mayn, mayn mame loshn

00:20:00.145 --> 00:20:01.877
host geleyent di tsaytungen?

00:20:02.575 --> 00:20:04.779
kh'hob geleyent zeyer veynik

00:20:04.836 --> 00:20:06.298
zeyer veynik geleyent.

00:20:06.928 --> 00:20:09.402
geleyent a yidishe tsaytung hob ikh geleyent.

00:20:10.590 --> 00:20:12.643
vi nokh hot geheysn di yidishe tsaytung?

00:20:10.793 --> 00:20:11.930
UNK

00:20:12.868 --> 00:20:17.536
 ver gedenkt dos? ikh gedenk gornisht vi di tsaytung hot geheysn.

00:20:19.787 --> 00:20:21.755
nu, JEWISH NEWS UNK gevezn.

00:20:23.112 --> 00:20:24.810
un bikher hostu geleyent?

00:20:24.580 --> 00:20:26.112
kh'hob geleyent bikher

00:20:26.112 --> 00:20:28.624
bin geven a MEMBER bin ikh geven

00:20:29.035 --> 00:20:32.589
in BETAR bin ikh gevezn

00:20:33.203 --> 00:20:34.969
a yunger tsienist.

00:20:35.295 --> 00:20:37.786
kh'hob zikh ongehoybn tsu lernen a bisl IVRIT

00:20:39.615 --> 00:20:41.291
un dos iz gevezn dos

00:20:41.291 --> 00:20:42.790
biz ⟨tsu di khasene⟩

00:20:41.590 --> 00:20:43.896
vi oft bistu gegangen in BETAR?

00:20:43.902 --> 00:20:45.094
nisht lang

00:20:45.488 --> 00:20:48.806
vayl ikh hob nisht keyn tsayt, gehat keyn tsayt ven tsu geyn

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:50.561
az ikh hob gearbet

00:20:50.938 --> 00:20:52.124
hob ikh gearbet

00:20:52.124 --> 00:20:54.746
tsvelef sho hob ikh gearbet a tog

00:20:55.174 --> 00:20:58.796
zol kenen oysarbetn di norme vos ikh hob gedorfn tsu fardinen.

00:20:58.819 --> 00:21:00.601
afilet fraytik

00:21:01.097 --> 00:21:03.515
iz nisht geven keyn gantser tog. s'iz geven

00:21:03.515 --> 00:21:06.289
vinter tsayt iz gevezn a kurtser tog

00:21:06.295 --> 00:21:07.616
hob ikh gemuzt geyn

00:21:07.616 --> 00:21:09.224
shabes oyf di nakht

00:21:09.990 --> 00:21:11.908
bin ikh geganen endikn di arbet.

00:21:11.948 --> 00:21:13.612
vos far a arbet hostu gemakht?

00:21:13.602 --> 00:21:14.493
kh'hob gemakht

00:21:14.493 --> 00:21:16.448
vinter arbet

00:21:16.521 --> 00:21:18.624
zhak- vinter zhaketn

00:21:21.617 --> 00:21:23.062
farshidene zakhn.

00:21:23.153 --> 00:21:25.239
kenst mir

00:21:25.667 --> 00:21:32.309
fartseyln vos, vos iz forgekumen bay di arbet, vos far a arbet, vi a- vi azoy host gearbet? di, di, di lage?

00:21:31.033 --> 00:21:35.212
kh'ho- kh'hob gea- kh'hob gearbet kinder antsegelekh hob ikh gearbet.

00:21:35.235 --> 00:21:38.351
kh'hob gearbet zhaketn. kh'hob gearbet

00:21:38.442 --> 00:21:41.726
mentl oykh gearbet. farshidene zakhn hob ikh gearbet.

00:21:41.479 --> 00:21:42.890
du host geneyt?

00:21:42.930 --> 00:21:46.518
geneyt un fertik gemakht. geneyt un ⟨opgeprest⟩.

00:21:48.938 --> 00:21:50.349
un bist geven feik?

00:21:50.271 --> 00:21:51.547
yo, yo.

00:21:51.908 --> 00:21:54.917
ikh hob fardint, ikh hob oysgeshoyr- geholfn

00:21:54.917 --> 00:21:57.673
di eltern hob ikh shoyn geholfn, biz tsu di khasene.

00:21:59.822 --> 00:22:02.111
iz ven hostu getrofn dayn froy?

00:22:02.337 --> 00:22:04.288
mayn froy hob ikh getrofn

00:22:04.851 --> 00:22:06.380
azoy in

00:22:06.673 --> 00:22:08.844
in finef un draysikstn yor.

00:22:09.205 --> 00:22:11.544
in Lodzh tsi in Pshedbuzh?

00:22:10.757 --> 00:22:11.628
Pshedbuzh.

00:22:12.310 --> 00:22:14.059
un zi iz oykh fun Pshedbuzh?

00:22:13.727 --> 00:22:14.463
yo.

00:22:14.149 --> 00:22:15.628
vi nokh hot zi geheysn?

00:22:15.482 --> 00:22:16.876
ZAIDBERG.

00:22:16.950 --> 00:22:18.277
un di ershte nomen?

00:22:18.537 --> 00:22:19.577
Yentl.

00:22:20.005 --> 00:22:23.171
kenst tseyln d- ZAIDBERG, v-

00:22:23.211 --> 00:22:26.698
yo, nu, shraybt UNK in di dos, in di dokumentn.

00:22:25.540 --> 00:22:27.795
ts- tseyl, tseyl iber vos i-

00:22:29.455 --> 00:22:31.946
Z.A.I.

00:22:32.256 --> 00:22:33.448
B.

00:22:34.011 --> 00:22:34.933
E.

00:22:38.010 --> 00:22:40.957
R. G. ZAIDBERG.

00:22:42.482 --> 00:22:43.120
mh

00:22:43.120 --> 00:22:44.804
vi lang

00:22:45.047 --> 00:22:48.281
zent ir gegangen tsuzamen farn, farn khasene makhn?

00:22:48.793 --> 00:22:49.681
kimat

00:22:49.873 --> 00:22:51.166
a yor tsayt.

00:22:53.046 --> 00:22:57.917
un mit ir mishpokhe bistu geven bakant? host zikh

00:22:57.265 --> 00:22:58.811
yo, yo.

00:22:58.868 --> 00:23:01.461
azoy UNK ikh bin avek fun mayn heym

00:23:02.935 --> 00:23:05.156
ikh bin arayn tsu ire eltern

00:23:05.314 --> 00:23:06.540
tsuzamen

00:23:07.947 --> 00:23:09.392
un ikh hob gearbet

00:23:09.516 --> 00:23:10.826
oyf a postn

00:23:11.035 --> 00:23:12.834
un zi hot gearbet in di heym.

00:23:13.009 --> 00:23:15.585
zi hot gearbet, zol kenen tsuhelfn di eltern

00:23:16.620 --> 00:23:18.824
vayl di eltern hobn nisht gehat keyn parnose.

00:23:19.152 --> 00:23:21.120
hob ikh gearbet in eyn zayt

00:23:21.430 --> 00:23:23.803
un zi hot gearbet tsu di tsveyte zayt

00:23:23.944 --> 00:23:25.316
azoy lang

00:23:25.316 --> 00:23:27.988
biz m'hot zikh tsunoyfgeredt, me zol khasene hobn

00:23:28.281 --> 00:23:31.869
vayl dos iz nisht geven keyn lebn. s'hot men gedorfn gebn parnose

00:23:31.993 --> 00:23:34.856
far akht mentshn. dos iz geven umgeherbar.

00:23:35.537 --> 00:23:39.075
in a kleyn shtetl oystsuarbetn far akht mentshn parnose

00:23:39.435 --> 00:23:41.437
hot men nisht gekent dos bahoyptn.

00:23:42.422 --> 00:23:43.951
m'hot khasene gehat

00:23:44.548 --> 00:23:46.148
un ⟨er hot mir⟩ ongeshribn

00:23:46.148 --> 00:23:47.124
a shtub.

00:23:47.755 --> 00:23:49.622
er hot gehat a hayzke hot er gehat

00:23:49.898 --> 00:23:51.360
fun fir tsimern.

00:23:52.041 --> 00:23:54.273
tsvey hot er avekgegebn a shvester

00:23:54.273 --> 00:23:57.468
un tsvey hot er zikh ibergelozt. hot er mir ongeshribn eyn shtub

00:23:57.610 --> 00:23:59.241
un di eyne shtub

00:23:59.770 --> 00:24:01.232
hob ikh farkoyft

00:24:01.930 --> 00:24:04.809
un zey ibergefirt keyn Lodzh.

00:24:05.625 --> 00:24:07.694
bay di Lodzh hob ikh zey ibergefirt

00:24:07.735 --> 00:24:10.007
hob ikh genumen a voynung tsuzamen

00:24:10.840 --> 00:24:12.322
m'hot gevoynt tsuzamen

00:24:12.322 --> 00:24:15.069
un dortn hobn zey ongehoybn tsu hobn parnose

00:24:15.328 --> 00:24:18.325
hot gehat d- tsvey kinder, yinglekh, BOYS

00:24:19.058 --> 00:24:22.984
vos zenen geven zeyer feike kinder. in Pshedbuzh hobn zey nisht gehat vos tsu tun.

00:24:23.226 --> 00:24:25.565
in Lodzh hobn zey ongehoybn tsu handlen

00:24:25.825 --> 00:24:28.370
oyfn mark, in di gasn

00:24:28.370 --> 00:24:30.999
mit knobl, mit tsibeles

00:24:31.258 --> 00:24:33.176
mit farshidene zakhn

00:24:33.435 --> 00:24:34.846
mit frukhtn

00:24:34.954 --> 00:24:37.293
un der foter hot oykhet

00:24:37.536 --> 00:24:38.846
gearbet

00:24:38.886 --> 00:24:40.787
hot gefirt in di ⟨heyf⟩

00:24:40.793 --> 00:24:41.985
IRAKOT.

00:24:42.227 --> 00:24:42.980
frukhtn.

00:24:43.662 --> 00:24:45.191
frukhtn, IRAKOT.

00:24:45.265 --> 00:24:47.604
un fun dem hobn zey gehat gut parnose

00:24:48.673 --> 00:24:51.350
shpeter, vi es, azoy vi der Hitler

00:24:51.390 --> 00:24:53.038
iz arayn keyn Poyln

00:24:53.635 --> 00:24:55.316
hot zikh dos ales geendert.

00:24:56.689 --> 00:24:58.910
hot zikh ongehoybn damolt di tsores.

00:24:59.929 --> 00:25:02.825
ikh hob gezen ikh ken nisht dortn farblaybn

00:25:03.102 --> 00:25:05.965
hob gezen voser tog iz erger un erger

00:25:06.578 --> 00:25:08.647
hob ikh bashtimt mit di froy

00:25:08.670 --> 00:25:10.014
az me zol antloyfn.

00:25:11.083 --> 00:25:14.030
zenen mir antlofn nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:25:14.391 --> 00:25:16.933
dos iz geven a geshikhte fun di

00:25:17.462 --> 00:25:19.121
⟨zog ikh⟩ rosheshone

00:25:19.121 --> 00:25:20.392
sukes tsayt

00:25:20.837 --> 00:25:22.603
in tsentn khoydesh

00:25:24.567 --> 00:25:27.075
oktober, november iz gevezn.

00:25:26.878 --> 00:25:34.089
far dem ho- hos-, hot ir zikh adurkhgeredt vegn, vegn vos, vos vet forkumen, vos

00:25:34.089 --> 00:25:34.773
vos

00:25:34.658 --> 00:25:38.347
m'hot nish- m'hot nisht farshtanen zikh vos adurkhtsuredn.

00:25:34.773 --> 00:25:35.698
pasirn?

00:25:38.590 --> 00:25:42.094
ven Hitler un di Hilterovtses zenen arayngekumen keyn Poyln

00:25:42.808 --> 00:25:46.644
hot men shoyn gemakht tsores. zey hobn shoyn aroysgenumen yidn

00:25:46.644 --> 00:25:48.000
fun di shtubn

00:25:48.276 --> 00:25:49.485
oyf arbet

00:25:50.166 --> 00:25:52.202
un hot geshlogn geharget.

00:25:52.680 --> 00:25:54.193
mikh hot di froy bahaltn.

00:25:55.583 --> 00:25:57.365
ikh bin nisht aroysgan in di gas arayn.

00:25:58.063 --> 00:25:59.272
zi hot mikh gedekt.

00:26:00.055 --> 00:26:01.618
vi hot zi dikh gedenkt?

00:26:01.303 --> 00:26:04.633
un di heym, ikh zol farblaybn in di heym, un mikh hot nisht gelozt UNK

00:26:04.633 --> 00:26:06.295
nisht in di reye nokh broyt.

00:26:06.295 --> 00:26:09.026
az s'iz geshtanen a por yidn in di reye nokh broyt

00:26:09.454 --> 00:26:12.401
hot men zey aroysgeshlept un gegebn a por kopyes, a por klep

00:26:12.711 --> 00:26:14.375
tseyogt un fertik.

00:26:16.660 --> 00:26:18.054
dos iz gevezn

00:26:18.752 --> 00:26:22.171
onheyb ven di, di Hitlerovtses zenen arayngekumen keyn Poyln.

00:26:26.228 --> 00:26:28.618
farn araynkumen in Poyln

00:26:29.097 --> 00:26:34.423
iz, iz epes pas- hot epes pasirt? s'iz geven bombardirn tsi vos?

00:26:33.973 --> 00:26:35.604
neyn, gornisht.

00:26:35.661 --> 00:26:37.173
gornisht gevezn.

00:26:38.142 --> 00:26:41.325
azoy vi zey zenen arayngekumen, hobn zey bombardirt in

00:26:41.533 --> 00:26:43.383
in Lodzh, in di shtot

00:26:43.862 --> 00:26:46.252
hobn zey ongevizn, dort gevezn

00:26:46.444 --> 00:26:49.087
di, di DEUTSCHEN NARODOWA.

00:26:49.380 --> 00:26:51.112
in land iz geven DEUTSCHEN.

00:26:51.237 --> 00:26:53.610
zey hobn ongevizn vu tsu bombardirn

00:26:54.375 --> 00:26:55.739
un dos iz gevezn.

00:26:55.739 --> 00:26:56.760
azoy

00:26:56.760 --> 00:26:59.026
m'hot zikh nor oysbahaltn in di shtubn.

00:26:59.488 --> 00:27:02.435
un shpeter, m'hot gezen az s'iz azoy shlekht

00:27:02.728 --> 00:27:04.747
hob ikh bashlosn mit di froy

00:27:04.905 --> 00:27:06.249
mir zoln avekforn.

00:27:05.968 --> 00:27:08.375
vifl shpeter hostu bashlosn dos?

00:27:08.365 --> 00:27:11.227
dos iz geven a geshikhte vi lang iz geven

00:27:11.267 --> 00:27:13.927
dortn di, di Hitlerovtses zenen gevezn

00:27:14.727 --> 00:27:16.577
a khoydesh, tsvey khadoshim

00:27:16.752 --> 00:27:18.636
nokh a tsvey khadoshim oykh nisht.

00:27:18.642 --> 00:27:21.758
kh'hob gezen s'heybt zikh on vos a molt erger un erger

00:27:22.607 --> 00:27:25.048
hot men bashlosn tsu, tsu antloyfn.

00:27:25.105 --> 00:27:27.377
ikh hob gevolt mitnemen ir foter

00:27:28.345 --> 00:27:31.801
mit di kinder hob ikh gevolt mitnemen, zogt er "vu" zogt er "vel ikh

00:27:31.801 --> 00:27:33.857
vel ikh mikh shlepn mit di kinder?"

00:27:34.369 --> 00:27:37.501
zog ikh "vu, vu undz vet men zikh shlepn, vestu dikh shlepn."

00:27:37.795 --> 00:27:40.573
er hot nisht gevolt forn, zenen mir undz avekgeforn

00:27:43.414 --> 00:27:45.753
un undz hot men oysgeshpilt beser

00:27:45.844 --> 00:27:48.285
un zey hobn gehat tsores iber di oyern.

00:27:48.342 --> 00:27:50.136
demolt hot zikh ongehoybn bay zey

00:27:50.136 --> 00:27:51.930
di rikhtike tsores.

00:27:55.311 --> 00:27:57.313
ven bist nokh geven in Lodzh

00:27:56.914 --> 00:27:57.819
yo

00:27:58.551 --> 00:28:03.354
hostu mit di, mit di eygene oygn gezen vos iz forgekumen?

00:28:03.647 --> 00:28:05.295
vos, tsu bayshpil?

00:28:04.575 --> 00:28:05.278
vo-

00:28:05.419 --> 00:28:08.518
vos host gezen antisemitishe aktsyes?

00:28:08.389 --> 00:28:10.897
mayn froy hot mikh nisht aroysgelozt.

00:28:11.545 --> 00:28:13.170
zi hot mikh oysbahaltn.

00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:15.994
zi iz ganen alts erleydikn in di gas

00:28:16.506 --> 00:28:20.027
gevust hob ikh, gezen hob ikh, az m'hot geyogt yidn

00:28:20.320 --> 00:28:23.672
aroys fun di reye. ikh bin ganen a por mol bin ikh ganen zen

00:28:23.948 --> 00:28:26.675
hob ikh gezen me makht zey groyse tsores

00:28:26.985 --> 00:28:28.450
bin ikh aheymgekumen

00:28:28.450 --> 00:28:30.776
hot mir di froy gezogt "gey nisht in di gas arayn.

00:28:30.833 --> 00:28:33.037
du zay do. ikh'l ales erleydikn."

00:28:33.398 --> 00:28:34.576
dos iz gevezn.

00:28:35.085 --> 00:28:36.904
m'vet oyfhern di tashme yetst.
